WEBVTT

00:04.413 --> 00:06.765
<i>National news network
How may I direct your call ?</i>

00:06.833 --> 00:09.141
There's going to be
an explosion this morning

00:09.240 --> 00:11.320
<i>- Excuse me ?</i>
- I said,

00:11.593 --> 00:14.002
there will be an explosion
this morning.

00:14.073 --> 00:15.220
A bomb.

00:15.293 --> 00:17.674
<i>Oh, Sorry.
Did you say a bomb, sir ?</i>

00:18.252 --> 00:20.087
<i>- Sir ?</i>
- On a bus...

00:20.604 --> 00:22.468
in the city where it all began.

00:22.593 --> 00:24.179
Get my message out.

00:24.256 --> 00:25.440
<i>Message ?</i>

00:25.673 --> 00:26.887
<i>What message ?</i>

00:27.156 --> 00:29.085
That this is only the beginning.

00:29.344 --> 00:31.516
Until it is brought back
under control,

00:33.249 --> 00:35.120
people will die.

