Hey ! Mornin', JJ.
How was your...

01:02.306 --> 01:03.553
weekend ?

01:04.848 --> 01:05.750
Yeah ?

01:05.767 --> 01:09.150
Homeland security just reported a bomb
threat for an unspecified urban area.

01:09.167 --> 01:10.732
It was phoned into
the national news network

01:10.758 --> 01:13.113
- I'll call you back. When ?
- Last half hour.

01:13.115 --> 01:15.553
- They need a threat assessment ASAP.
- Get the team together.

01:15.566 --> 01:16.482
Yeah.

01:17.835 --> 01:20.192
<i>I'm sorry,
Did you say a bomb, sir ?</i>

01:20.438 --> 01:21.562
<i>On a bus...</i>

01:21.576 --> 01:23.171
<i>in the city where it all began.</i>

01:23.396 --> 01:24.723
<i>Get my message out.</i>

01:24.736 --> 01:26.901
<i>Message ?
What message ?</i>

01:27.255 --> 01:29.222
<i>That this is only the beginning.<i></i></i>

01:29.635 --> 01:31.770
<i>Until it is brought back
under control,</i>

01:32.116 --> 01:33.923
<i>people will die.</i>

01:35.215 --> 01:36.663
In the last 20 minutes,

01:36.677 --> 01:38.771
virtually identical threats
have been made

01:38.785 --> 01:41.583
to most of the coast-to-coast
news networks in the country.

01:41.747 --> 01:44.751
It's the same information
just slightly different words.

01:44.965 --> 01:46.972
So it's not a recorded
message or script.

01:46.987 --> 01:48.581
Displays a measure of confidence.

01:48.596 --> 01:50.610
He could have easily
just called one network.

01:50.628 --> 01:52.571
This guy obviously wants attention.

01:52.588 --> 01:55.271
It's typical behavior
for a personal cause bomber.

01:56.288 --> 01:59.762
One bomb has a finite impact.
It's just a little package.

02:00.145 --> 02:03.502
Make bunch of phone calls,
that magnifies my explosion 100 times.

02:03.627 --> 02:06.690
We have the additional recorded calls
being gathered for assessment.

02:06.887 --> 02:09.252
Networks say the calls came
from a restricted number.

02:09.268 --> 02:11.483
Two have given limited permission
to trap and trace

02:11.486 --> 02:13.332
the lines if we should need to.

02:13.368 --> 02:15.780
You got a news organization
to agree to a trap and trace ?

02:15.797 --> 02:16.970
Who could say "no" to me ?

02:16.985 --> 02:19.792
This is not likely Al-Qaeda. They don't
call unless they bomb something.

02:19.807 --> 02:22.941
At Homeland security's request,
the networks are going to keep this quiet

02:22.957 --> 02:25.952
- until we've assessed the situation.
- It doesn't feel like a hoax.

02:26.245 --> 02:29.510
His voice is calm, resigned. He's made
his decision. He's committed to it.

02:29.668 --> 02:32.583
Plus he said :
"This is only the beginning"

02:32.858 --> 02:34.560
The beginning of what ?
And he also said :

02:34.577 --> 02:38.000
"until it is brought back
under control". What's it ?

02:38.136 --> 02:40.751
He has to call back. And if this threat
isn't followed by an event,

02:40.768 --> 02:42.942
no one will take
any future calls seriously.

02:43.105 --> 02:45.853
So, we're going to tell the media
to go ahead with the story ?

02:45.866 --> 02:47.193
Absolutely not.

02:47.208 --> 02:50.081
Threats like this,
with an unspecified location

02:50.106 --> 02:52.053
will just cause tremendous panic.

02:52.376 --> 02:54.470
Then, what are we gonna do ?

02:57.177 --> 02:59.743
Unfortunately,
all we can do is wait.

